# ZAP-DESK — Project Rules

Monorepo: **ZAP-DESK** (Qt6/C++20) + **Reconner** (Python in `reconner/`).

## Principles

- UI in `src/ui/` — orchestration only, no domain logic
- ZAP REST API only via `ZapClient`
- Recon only via `ReconRunner` → `python3 -m reconner`
- Paths via `AppConfig` — never hardcode `/data/dev/...`
- Recon requires authorization checkbox in UI before execution
- **All docs, UI strings, and comments in English** (see `english-only.mdc`)

## Structure

```
src/config/     → AppConfig (env, XDG paths)
src/core/       → ZapClient, ZapDaemon
src/services/   → ReconRunner, ReconBridge, ZapUpdater
src/ui/         → MainWindow (90s hacker theme)
reconner/       → vendored Python engine
docs/           → ARCHITECTURE.md, ROADMAP.md, ZAP-INSTALL-LINUX.md
```

## Main flow

BOOT ZAP → RUN RECON (--proxy) → FEED ZAP (summary.json) → ACTIVE SCAN

